C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>co\u003Cunclear>l\u003C/unclear>\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>onia\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cname>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Hel\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>via\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>\u003Cname>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Aug\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>usta\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/name> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003CorgName>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Lilybit\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>anorum\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/orgName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>devota \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> numini\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\"/>eorum \n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>text of CIL\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#AR\">\n                \u003Cp>A [...] pio, felice, augusto, la comunità di Lilibeo della Colonia Helvia Augusta devota al loro Genio (ha predisposto questo)\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#AR\">\n                \u003Cp>To [...] pious, fortunate augustus, the Lilybetan government of the Colony of Helvia Augusta faithful to their Genius (set this up)\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--(f)el aug / res p co(l) hel(u) / aug lilybit / devota numini / eorum. Sartori, F. Le dodici tribu di Lilibeo, in Kokalos 1957, 3, pp.38-60: Primarily on issue of constitutional organisation from time of Caesar onwards, but therefore considers in depth the development of organisation etc. from the pre-Republican period onwards, as well as questions of Roman policy on the matter. Note Manganaro 1979, p.422 and n.42, which cites a number of relevant pieces for the discussion both pre and post dating this article. Mentioned in Manganaro 1988: 19-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Gualtherus\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1624\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>232\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GIN6NANU\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Gualtherus\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1624 [1625]\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>124\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/ZP8DE8KS\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\">7205\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Sartori\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1957\u003C/date>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/PHEH2TTF\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001604\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001604\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1988\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>19\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RZSFKACR\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
